snippet.title: Final Battle 「Phrenapates」 Piano M/V / Blue archive OST Theme 156 「Final Destination of Ark」
snippet.description:
Blue Archive - Final Chapter OST 「Final Destination of Ark」 "Theme 156" Piano Performance


Today's performance is the final battle (Showdown) with "Phrenapates" that marks the end of the first part of the story.
This is “Theme 156” 「Final Destination of Ark」.

It is a truly attractive song with a melody that gives off a majestic yet sorrowful feeling.
In particular, when you first hear this song, you will fall in love with the grandeur of the final boss battle.
It is a song that makes you feel the despair and sadness rather than the grandeur after going through the entire story.

There was no piano part at all, but I wanted to capture that sublime yet sad melody in grandeur.
A part of the famous song "Myosotis", which can make you feel sad and intense emotions, is quoted in the intro.

The video tells the biography of from “Reunion with Kuroko” to “Escape from the Ark.”
I captured it with scenes from the final battle and made it into a music video format.

Thank you for listening.

Discord Channel : https://discord.gg/TGvwJR9rs7
Twitch Streaming : https://www.twitch.tv/frost_piano

Blue Archive 1st Anniversary PV OST(Luminous Memory) Piano Play : https://youtu.be/1xhW91bbFS8
